com.petpet.c3po.command
Interface Command

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractCLICommand, ExportCommand, GatherCommand, HelpCommand, ProfileCommand, RemoveCommand, SamplesCommand, VersionCommand
public interface Command

A command interface for the CLI. It denotes a mode in which the C3PO CLI can operate.

Author:
Petar Petrov

Method Detail

setParams

void setParams(Params params)
Sets the parameter for the command (that were passed on the command line).

Parameters:
params - the params to set.

execute

void execute()
Called if everything was ok and should execute the current command. Note that the setParams(Params) method will be called exactly once before calling this method. The method should optionally record its time for execution (where needed) and return it in getTime().

getTime

long getTime()
Retrieves the time needed for the execution of this command in milliseconds. If the command does not require time tracking, then -1 is returned.

Returns:
the time needed for this command to execute.
